label: Thinkers Magazine
title: Thinkers_Magazine
exrest: Thinkers Magazine is a monthly magazine based in Abuja, Nigeria. Thinkers Magazine is a sister publication of the daily online-based Thinkers Newspaper published by Thinkers Communications Limited. Thinkers Communications Limited was established in 2008 in Abuja, Nigeria.
